# Vertical Slice Delivery

Each implementation slice MUST include:

1. Domain logic (`packages/domain`, `packages/application`)
2. Persistence adapter (`packages/adapters`)
3. API endpoint (`apps/api`) or worker task (`apps/worker`)
4. Authorization check at application-service boundary
5. Audit event for mutating operations
6. Tests (unit minimum; integration for adapters)
7. Alembic migration if schema changes
8. Minimal UI surface in `apps/web` when user-visible

Do not implement "API only" or "DB only" slices. Link changes to MVP requirement IDs (e.g. MVP-01) or epic IDs (e.g. EPIC-02).

## Change package (include in PR/commit description)

- Summary and linked requirements
- Design notes and ADR references
- Changed files list
- Tests added/updated
- Migrations and rollback notes
- Risks and unresolved questions
